{"tid":2243575,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"求救：M42-OM 轉接環","createTime":"2020-10-15T00:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T11:17:18.000Z","uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1dd8387108d328b60aa9f48ca1c9ec8077fd2d","tid":2243575,"uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"話說買咗部Olympus OM 10 菲林相機學玩菲林相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRchrdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRchrdN.jpg&h=1e82d25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我自己本身都有枝HELIOS-44M-4 2/58mm <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHRmSUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHRmSUi.jpg&h=373e0d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗住菲林機配老鏡一流🤤 然後我就搵咗好耐入手呢個轉接環 M42-OM<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4L62Cmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4L62Cmk.jpg&h=1ec150a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連接機身能夠對位插得入 但固定唔到鏡頭 360度旋轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且個環同機身頂唔到鏡頭個控制光圈嗰粒掣(紅圈)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymtko3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fymtko3c.jpg&h=65d5edb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變相即係控制唔到光圈，甚至連無限遠都對唔到焦。<br />\n（法蘭距唔啱所致）<br />\n所以想向大家求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知道M42-OM轉接環係冇廠出？<br />\n<br />\n手機排版*"},{"pid":"f4ee0d67dfb90f292ef2bbac2d154f5ecc3b5827","tid":2243575,"uid":22310,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"你呢個to OM應該for 無反？"},{"pid":"a77a1d5525c21275da4ee07aec8f0b182